嗨家教(Hi家教) 線上英語師資群介紹


 












哲學一把罩！書香佳人 Angelica (安潔莉卡) 老師











 聽聽線上英文老師的聲音





 


This  is Angelica. I graduated from the University of Santo Tomas with a degree in AB  Philosophy.
我是Angelica。畢業於Santo Tomas大學的哲學系。 
There  are many activities to kill our free time; I prefer to spend mine by reading. I  especially love sitting back and enjoying mystery novels, Japanese comic books,  and philosophy books. I quite disagree when people say reading means we are not  socializing because whatever I read I can share it with people who are  interested. 

                                消磨時間的方式往往因人而異；對我而言，『閱讀』是我消磨時間的方式。我喜歡沉浸在推理小說、日本漫畫和哲學的世界裡，並藉以放鬆自己。有些人說『閱讀』沒有社交，我不認同這樣的說法，因為不管在書上看到了什麼有趣的東西，我都樂於提出來和同好分享。 

                                I  often like to immerse myself in foreign cultures through music, TV programs and  films so that I can expand my horizon and appreciate the beauty of the world.  In addition, I can share what I’ve learned with my students. In my class, I  always encourage my students by telling them that the more time you spend with  the language, the faster you will learn.   Spending enough time on the language makes it easier to incorporate it  in one’s everyday life. That is the greatest guarantee of success.

                                我常常透過國外的音樂、電視節目和電影，讓自己沉浸在異國文化之中，一方面拓展我的視野，一方面欣賞這個世界美好的一面。此外，我還能在課堂中和學生一起分享這些有趣的事物。另外，我總是鼓勵學生～外語是越用，越靈光。不管任何語言學習，一定需要投註相對的時間，並將其融入日常生活，才是語言學習成功的保證。 

                                When  it comes to teaching, I try to conduct high quality classes all the time. I’d  like to think I’m flexible so I try to teach in a way that best suits the  student’s comprehension. I have taught students from all ages. (Their ages  range from 7 to 52.) If the student wants advanced lessons, then I try to  oblige them. If the student is a low beginner, I do my best to ask easy  questions and make him/her comfortable with talking to me.

                                在英文教學的方面，我追求高品質的教學成效。我期許自己在英文教學上要有彈性，並透過因材施教、適時調整自己的教學方式，以確保學生能夠充分理解課程內容。我的學生各個年齡層都有 (從7歲到52歲)。如果學生想要上更進階的英文課程，我一定全力配合。當然，如果學生是初學者，我會透過簡單的英文問答，讓他們能夠更輕鬆自在的交談。 

                                I  place a lot of emphasis on the basics – pronunciation, vocabulary, grammar, and  syntax,
                                because  I believe they are the foundation of a language. Through our online courses,  you will have a good grasp of English, and you'll find it easier to master it.  Your fluency, speed and accent are developed gradually over time. All you need  to do is focus on the basics and everything else will fall into place. 

                                我非常強調語言基礎能力的養成—從英文發音、英文字彙、英文文法都是，因為這些是學習語言的基礎。透過我們的線上英文課程，你將會理解英文，並發現透過這種方式是比較容易精熟英文的。一段時間之後，你在英文會話的流暢度、速度和口音就會進步很多。
                                所以，剛開始只要先專註在打好語言的基礎，其他的一切就會水到渠成。 
Teaching  Experience (Year): 6 years
英文教學經驗：六年 
Target  Students:  Level 2 - Level 9
適合學生程度： 2級– 9級 
Teaching  Professional Specialty: 
                                Vocabulary, Pronunciation, Grammar, Daily Conversation,  & Literature 
英文教學專長：英文字彙、英文發音、英文文法、日常英文會話、英文文學。 




 







